            <div class="flex justify-between" title="Total monthly bills during construction (lease + bank construction interest + current building)"><span class="text-stone-500">Monthly cost during build</span><span id="cBurden" class="mono font-semibold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between border-t border-stone-200 pt-2" title="What's left over each month after paying everything during construction"><span class="font-medium">Are we covered during build?</span><span id="cDeficit" class="mono font-bold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between mt-2" title="The mortgage payment after we exercise the option-to-buy and refinance"><span class="text-stone-500">Mortgage after we buy</span><span id="cPerm" class="mono font-semibold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between" title="What's left over after the new mortgage payment"><span class="text-stone-500">Are we covered after we buy?</span><span id="cPermDef" class="mono font-bold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-dashed border-stone-200" title="The building must appraise for at least this much for the bank to refinance"><span class="text-stone-500">Building must appraise for</span><span id="cArvNeeded" class="mono font-semibold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between" title="How much room we have between the appraisal we expect and the appraisal we need"><span class="text-stone-500">Room above what bank requires</span><span id="cRefiGap" class="mono font-bold">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between" title="Yes = bank will refinance. No = we walk away from the lease (no money lost)."><span class="font-semibold">Will the bank refinance?</span><span id="cRefiClears" class="font-bold uppercase text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">--</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between mt-1" title="Income divided by payment. 1.0 = exactly enough. 1.2+ = bank likes it. Below 1.0 = we can't afford it."><span class="text-stone-500">Income vs payment ratio</span><span id="cDscr" class="mono font-semibold">--</span></div>
          </div>
          <div id="cStory" class="mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-[color:var(--line)] text-[12px] text-stone-700 leading-relaxed bg-[color:var(--mist)] -mx-5 -mb-5 px-5 py-3 rounded-b-2xl"></div>
        </div>

