        <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-4">Nine independent revenue streams. Each tier de-risks the prior. Conservative is the appropriate underwriting basis.</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-stone-200">
                <th class="text-left py-2 font-semibold">Layer</th>
                <th class="text-right py-2 font-semibold">Monthly gross</th>
